Commands to install prerequisites in ubuntu 14.04:

#To install python
$sudo apt-get install python

#To install java
$sudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jdk

#To install pip
sudo apt-get install python-pip

#To install python-dev
sudo apt-get install python-dev

#To install sentiment_classifier, NLTK, Numpy, SentiWordNet
sudo pip install sentiment_classifier

#To install libsvm
sudo apt-get install python-libsvm
